OL,6,FThere are fears that junior doctors in
OL,7,FJersey may avoid requesting scans that
OL,8,Fpatients need due to the "aggressive"
OL,9,Fnature of colleagues.
OL,11,FThe concerning revelation forms part
OL,12,Fof an expert report by The Royal
OL,13,FCollege of Radiologists about the
OL,14,Fisland's General Hospital.
OL,16,FIt states concerns that "behaviour is
OL,17,Fsometimes so aggressive ... a doctor's
OL,18,Fclinical judgement may change over
OL,19,Ftime, such that they opt
