OL,6,Fnot to request a scan (to avoid
OL,7,Fconfrontation) and this subsequently
OL,8,Fleads to adverse
OL,10,Foutcomes for patients."
OL,12,FThe review details hearing "multiple
OL,13,Freports of 'rough treatment' of junior
OL,14,Fdoctors when they come to radiology
OL,15,Fwith requests for imaging" and that
OL,16,Fthese asks appear to be considered
OL,17,F"without due regard to professional
OL,18,Fcourtesy and civility".
