OL,3,CFears that doctors avoid patient scans
OL,4,Cdue to 'aggressive' radiologists
OL,6,FParticular concerns were raised over
OL,7,Fpatient safety in cases where
OL,8,Fradiologists refused to carry out head
OL,9,FCT scans which would have been
OL,10,Fjustified in other hospitals,
OL,11,Faccording to the report.
OL,13,FThe review team say they heard a
OL,14,Fnumber of examples of junior doctors
OL,15,Fbeing spoken to inappropriately and
OL,16,Fmore than one person indicated that
OL,17,Fthis was a particular issue for female
OL,18,Fmembers of staff.
