OL,3,CFears that doctors avoid patient scans
OL,4,Cdue to 'aggressive' radiologists
OL,6,FEven more concerningly, the experts
OL,7,Fexplain they were told that after one
OL,8,Ffemale junior doctor raised a formal
OL,9,Fcomplaint, the staff member was
OL,10,F"advised
OL,12,Fto avoid going to the radiology
OL,13,Fdepartment in the future".
OL,15,FThe findings note problems over three
OL,16,Fyears, including in the department
OL,17,Fitself with a "them and us culture
OL,18,Fbetween radiologists and radiographic
OL,19,Fstaff".
