OL,3,CFears that doctors avoid patient scans
OL,4,Cdue to 'aggressive' radiologists
OL,6,FThe review was commissioned after a
OL,7,Fstaff member at Jersey Hospital raised
OL,8,Fconcerns over a radiologist's work -
OL,9,Fit was subsequently revealed that a
OL,10,Fhandful of women were told their
OL,11,Fmammograms were clear when in fact
OL,12,Fthey had breast cancer.
OL,14,FThat doctor is still employed in the
OL,15,Fdepartment under restricted duties -
OL,16,FThe Royal College of Radiologists
OL,17,Fbelieves they should not be involved
OL,18,Fin reading scans.
