OL,6,FIt has made a number of other
OL,7,Frecommendations, such as creating a
OL,8,Fone-stop breast clinic to stop delays
OL,9,Ffor patients seeking support,
OL,10,Fdiagnosis and treatment.
OL,12,FIn response to the report, Chris Bown,
OL,13,FChief Officer of Jersey's Health and
OL,14,FCommunity Services, says: "The wider
OL,15,Fconcerns raised by the Royal College
OL,16,Fof Radiologists make for sobering
OL,17,Freading.
OL,19,F"It is clear we need to reset the
OL,20,Frelationship between
